      <title>伯克希尔的营业利润跃升为保险，利率提高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/berkshire-hathaway-s-operating-profit-jumps-as-rates-lift-income</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）的运营收益在第四季度飙升了71％，因为较高的利率提高了该集团的投资收入及其保险业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/berkshire-hathaway-s-operating-profit-jumps-as-rates-lift-income</guid>
